Description.Text:
Property Location
With a stay at Nova Platinum Hotel in Pattaya (South Pattaya), you'll be minutes from Walking Street and close to Pattaya Pier. This 4-star hotel is within close proximity of Pattaya Hill and Ripley's Believe It or Not.

Rooms
Make yourself at home in one of the 270 air-conditioned rooms featuring refrigerators and minibars. Premium TV channels and DVD players are provided for your entertainment. Bathrooms feature showers, complimentary toiletries, and hair dryers. Conveniences include safes and desks, and housekeeping is provided daily.

Rec, Spa, Premium Amenities
Dip into one of the 2 outdoor swimming pools or enjoy other recreational amenities including a sauna and a fitness center. This hotel also features complimentary wireless Internet access and tour/ticket assistance.

Dining
Enjoy a meal at a restaurant, or stay in and take advantage of the hotel's 24-hour room service. Thirsty? Quench your thirst at a bar/lounge, a poolside bar, or a swim-up bar.

Business, Other Amenities
Featured amenities include a 24-hour business center, limo/town car service, and express check-in.


Pets not allowed Check-in time starts at 2 PM Check-out time is noon
